    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">父</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ちゝ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぎみはしはぶき二つ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">母</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はゝ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぎみはそよ一<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">雫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しづく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">瀬戸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">せど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の海、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">東</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひがし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をさしし<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">三日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>まへに我を見ましぬ。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">世馴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れざる野がくれわらべ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">手文筥</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">てふばこ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">封</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>じもあへず、<lb />
ゐざり<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">出</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">い</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>て<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">閾</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しきゐ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">端</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">柱</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はしら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">抱</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">だ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">面</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おもて</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かくしぬ。<lb />
<lb />
いとほしや<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">小</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ちさ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">学生</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">がくしやう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
いくとせを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">東</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あづま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">京</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きやう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">旅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">寝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">い</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ね<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">旅</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にねざめて<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">文</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のわざいそしまむとや。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">口</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">軽</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">胸</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">むね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">冷</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>やけき <lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">旅館女</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はたごめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の待遇ぶりに、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">慨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なげ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>きては、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">雨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夕</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆうべ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">欄</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">らん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、おゝ、何のおもひで。<lb />
<lb />
いとほし、と涙もろに、<lb />
叔母ぎみは<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">守袋</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まもりぶくろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<lb />
てづからにやさしうかけて、<lb />
わが<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">背</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">せな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をそと<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">撫</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>でましぬ。<lb />
<lb />
をりから<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">車</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くるま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">気近</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">けぢか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>う、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">婢女</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はしため</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">荷</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">に</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をとゝのふれば、<lb />
父ぎみはいとおごそかに<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">健</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">けん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なれ、とそれよ一言。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">母</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はゝ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぎみよ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">乳母</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うば</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>よ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">叔母</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">をば</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ぎみ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">朝露</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あさつゆ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に五<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">町</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">てふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">濡</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぬ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れ来て<lb />
さらばよの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御声</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おんこゑ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ごえや、<lb />
やわらかにその尾をいきて<lb />
野の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鶏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の声も流れつ。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
